BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Wit & Wisdom
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260716T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260716T213000
DTSTAMP:20260711T043903Z
UID:occ-1656@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Cabaret
DESCRIPTION:Three Smoke on the Mountain castmates sing Broadway's roles fo
 r grown-ups — 30 seats\, 21 and up.\n\nJeff Cooper\, Blaine Clotfelter\,
  and Vickie Zuffoletti\, last together in the Strand's 2024 Smoke on the M
 ountain\, reunite for a set of songs written for the Broadway canon's deci
 dedly non-ingenue characters — the wisdom and humor that come with age\,
  sung by people who have it. Zuffoletti curates and hosts the Lumiere Loun
 ge Cabaret Series\, of which this is part. Seating is capped at 30\, each 
 ticket includes a drink ticket\, and the room is 21 and up\; the lounge st
 ays open after the show.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260711T043436Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 07Eti9MAC
END:VEVENT
