BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Luke Null
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260724T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260724T211500
DTSTAMP:20260711T043903Z
UID:occ-927@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Stand-up Comedy
DESCRIPTION:Musical comedy from a former SNL featured player — dirty son
 gs\, catchy hooks\, 90 minutes\, no intermission.\n\nLuke Null does stand-
 up with a guitar: filthy lyrics set to melodies that stick\, a style he bu
 ilt in Chicago clubs before a season as a featured player on Saturday Nigh
 t Live. His 2024 special\, "Pretty Songs\, Dirty Words\," now free on YouT
 ube\, tells you exactly what you're in for. Part of the Comedy at The Stra
 nd series. 90 minutes\, no intermission.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260711T043436Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 06X8wDMAS
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Grease Sing-A-Long (1978)
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260801T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260801T170000
DTSTAMP:20260711T043903Z
UID:occ-1233@atlcal.com
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:The 1978 movie musical with on-screen lyrics — sing every wo
 rd\, rated PG\, 105 minutes.\n\nThe 1978 film with John Travolta and Olivi
 a Newton-John as Danny and Sandy\, screened sing-along style with on-scree
 n lyrics for "Summer Nights\," "Greased Lightnin'\," and the rest. A summe
 r romance collides with 1950s high-school social order when the pair land 
 at the same school. Rated PG\, 1 hour 45 minutes\, and a live pre-show con
 cert on the house Mighty Allen Theatre Organ begins thirty minutes before 
 the film.
GEO:33.9536122;-84.5492054
LAST-MODIFIED:20260711T043436Z
LOCATION:The Strand Theatre\, 117 N Park Square
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
URL:https://thestrand.my.salesforce-sites.com/ticket/#/instances/a0FPs0000
 0749iDMAQ
END:VEVENT
