CATEGORIES:Film Screening
DESCRIPTION:Disney's 1964 classic with Julie Andrews\, preceded by a live 
 concert on the Mighty Allen Theatre Organ.\n\nThe 1964 Disney musical that
  made Julie Andrews a movie star: a practically perfect nanny descends on 
 the Banks children of Edwardian London\, with Dick Van Dyke's chimney swee
 p Bert along for "Chim Chim Cher-ee\," "A Spoonful of Sugar\," and the res
 t. Rated G\, 2 hours 19 minutes. A live pre-show concert on the house's Mi
 ghty Allen Theatre Organ starts thirty minutes before the film. Note: a co
 ncurrent Glover Park Concert closes North and East Park Streets\, so parki
 ng in the Waddell deck is advised.
